{"tid":1905602,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[我阿婆都屌打] 巴塞今晚仲諗住拎咩人出黎打皇馬？","createTime":"2020-03-01T11:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T14:50:45.000Z","uid":90515,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c3645cbde8336460d18ab53da21a44e3cdd3bcbb","tid":1905602,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:06:58.000Z","msg":"前鋒<br />\n<br />\n蘇9: 傷出，5月見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n丹比利: 傷出，8月見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基沙文: 仲適應緊中鋒位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n法迪: 得17歲，毛都未生齊<br />\n美斯: 老<br />\n比夫韋治: 前魚腩隊射手，入隊2個禮拜都無<br />\n<br />\n中場<br />\n<br />\n布斯基斯: 公園廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉傑迪: 未賣已經偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n艾法: 勁勁地，但無防守能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n迪莊: 有得踢防中再講<br />\n蘿拔圖: 傷出，過多2個禮拜再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n維度: 上場條仆街先拎完紅牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後衛<br />\n<br />\n艾巴: 尋晚先medical green<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n碧基: 前日先medical green<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢普: 上場失球戰犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n烏迪迪: 唔夠高嘅力加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朗格列: 算合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n施美度: 勁勁地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n堂堂巴塞揾11個正常人出黎踩下草地都咁勉強，係對拿坡里呢啲意甲都踢唔掂嘅球隊先偷到個和，仲要對上10次歐聯作客入3球失18球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。皇馬雖然上場輸俾鏝城，但個陣容點都好過巴幾條街，主場贏巴狗幾球係基本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca785fc23d943ef21dc1de57fc7c21416571084f","tid":1905602,"uid":117037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:09:15.000Z","msg":"岩岩賣左個腎allin落皇馬到<br />\n聽日可以買返兩個返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5161560bdc6c565070d6e8a39c2126e2088e5ed","tid":1905602,"uid":7917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:09:20.000Z","msg":"我皇必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d67d6898a7fa7ee70949aa4e937e98169a551b","tid":1905602,"uid":80122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:11:19.000Z","msg":"vidal上場西甲紅左？"},{"pid":"36ad8859f2c690d058278fa1e4628bf5057c8186","tid":1905602,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7d67d6898a7fa7ee70949aa4e937e98169a551b","tid":1905602,"uid":80122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:11:19.000Z","msg":"vidal上場西甲紅左？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:12:03.000Z","msg":"條on9歐聯發皮4被人紅左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd8993d15cb47ab6f994e9810ec0d10e8e20f08","tid":1905602,"uid":134997,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:13:18.000Z","msg":"巴狗肉酸到要學利狗燈自己"},{"pid":"a0ab3e37b8cc7b15b16841fa6022cdde54e537aa","tid":1905602,"uid":80122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:13:45.000Z","msg":"出飛普實仆街"},{"pid":"4a07bdadb5f062c58cdfe32f523516207e559ae6","tid":1905602,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcd8993d15cb47ab6f994e9810ec0d10e8e20f08","tid":1905602,"uid":134997,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:13:18.000Z","msg":"巴狗肉酸到要學利狗燈自己"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:16:04.000Z","msg":"有講錯咩，成隊傷N個人，無傷嘅就年紀大，唔係年紀大就年紀太細，當打之年嘅就唔啱位，當打又啱位嘅又踢唔掂，當打啱位踢得掂嘅又脾氣唔好食紅左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc01996ba22b3332be92b933dd85565fc2b045d","tid":1905602,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0